  eudi_qeaa -- OpenID4VCI --- eudi_wallet
  gbo -- GraphQL --- eudi_asi & eudi_pubeaa & oots_adapter & dvtp_afnemer & ebw_qerds_adapter & g2g_adapter
  eudi_asi ~~~ eudi_pubeaa -- OpenID4VCI ---- eudi_wallet
  oots_adapter -- REST-JSON --- oots_basis
  oots_basis -- eDelivery-AS4 --- oots_afnemer
  gbo -- REST-JSON<br/>(PIP) --- dvtp_toestemming
  dvtp_toestemming -- REST-JSON --- dvtp_afnemer
  dvtp_toestemming -- REST-JSON --- dvtp_pseudoniem
  dvtp_pseudoniem ~~~ dvtp_afnemer
  ebw_qerds_adapter -- QERDS API / eDelivery-AS4 --- ebw_pub_qtsp -- QERDS delivery flow --- ebw_wallet
  ebw_qerds_adapter -- QERDS API / eDelivery-AS4 --- ebw_qtsp -- QERDS delivery flow --- ebw_wallet
  eudi_wallet --- burger["Burger"]
  oots_afnemer --- burger
  dvtp_afnemer --- burger
  ebw_wallet --- organisatie["Organisatie<br/>(publiek/privaat)"]
  g2g_adapter -- GraphQL / REST-JSON --- g2g_fsc
  g2g_adapter ~~~ ebw_qtsp
  ebw_qtsp ~~~ g2g_fsc
  g2g_fsc --- overheid["Ketenpartner<br/>(overheid)"]

